						<summary>

						<p>On a stone built into the wall of the Mūlaṅkūri temple.</p>						

						<p>Records the gift of land by Maṅgana Voḍayalu for the merit of the king <hi rend="italic">(Rāyalu)</hi> and the commanders, to the <hi rend="italic">Sthānapati</hi> Sūrana as <hi rend="italic">sarvamānya</hi> for the worship of the goddess Mūlaṅgūramma.</p>						

